<subSubSection id="C34AA094FFCDF13D42C8685FFC62FA6E" pageId="4" pageNumber="505" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BEFF31FFFCDF13D42C8685FFB15FAF2" blockId="4.[151,1437,331,1509]" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">
<emphasis id="B9242F0DFFCDF13D42C8685FFEC3FADE" bold="true" box="[199,308,1339,1365]" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">Remarks</emphasis>
. The median clypeal lobe of this species is well developed in comparison to other species of the subfamily. The mandibles of the German female were not examined because of their preservation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEFF31FFFCDF13D42C868E7FC62FA6E" blockId="4.[151,1437,331,1509]" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">
<taxonomicName id="4C50889CFFCDF13D42C868E7FE13FA16" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1809" box="[199,484,1411,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Sclerodermus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="505" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="domesticus">
<emphasis id="B9242F0DFFCDF13D42C868E7FE13FA16" box="[199,484,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">Sclerodermus domesticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the 
<typeStatus id="54EB4DBDFFCDF13D403F68E0FD97FA15" box="[560,608,1412,1438]" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">type</typeStatus>
species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C50889CFFCDF13D40D068E7FC8FFA16" authorityName="Latreille. The" authorityYear="1809" box="[735,888,1411,1437]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Sclerodermus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="505" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9242F0DFFCDF13D40D068E7FC8FFA16" box="[735,888,1411,1437]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">Sclerodermus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It has a confusing nomenclatural history, which sometimes was misattributed to Klug in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC18EEEFFCDF13D406D68C3FCE1FA4A" author="Latreille, P. A." box="[610,790,1447,1473]" pageId="4" pageNumber="505" refId="ref12049" refString="Latreille, P. A. (1809) Genera Crustaceorum et Insectorum secundum ordinem naturalem in familias desposita, iconibus exemplisque plurimis explicata. Vol. 4. Armand Konig. Parisiis et Argentorati (Paris &amp; Strasbourg). 399 pp." type="book" year="1809">Latreille (1809)</bibRefCitation>
. However, Pujade 
<emphasis id="B9242F0DFFCDF13D41E468CCFBEAFA4A" box="[1003,1053,1447,1473]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="505">et al</emphasis>
. (2021) clarified the problem and properly concluded the authorship of this species is 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC18EEEFFCDF13D40D268AFFC67FA6E" author="Latreille, P. A." box="[733,912,1483,1509]" pageId="4" pageNumber="505" refId="ref12049" refString="Latreille, P. A. (1809) Genera Crustaceorum et Insectorum secundum ordinem naturalem in familias desposita, iconibus exemplisque plurimis explicata. Vol. 4. Armand Konig. Parisiis et Argentorati (Paris &amp; Strasbourg). 399 pp." type="book" year="1809">Latreille (1809)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
